&quot;Vasilissa, I have found a perfect place for our attack.  We should go and ready it before the sun sets.&quot;  Marpe reported. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 791<br> <font color=#993300>(2/25/03 9:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=67>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The men.</span><hr size=1> &quot;Good..then let's go.  Marpe lead us to the spot,&quot; Hippolyte said..eager to get everything ready.  She followed Marpe into the dark forest and to the spot.  After some decision...it was decided where they would dig the gopher holes.    Hippolyte grabbed a large spade and dug away at the hole. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

