<br>
Glancing up at the familiar wolf, Marpe nodded in respect to it.  She knew the Scynthian wolves were unlike any others.  Like small shamans, they seemed to work along side the amazons of the northern lands.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 796<br> <font color=#993300>(2/27/03 10:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=71>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The men.</span><hr size=1> Now deep in the hole, Hippolyte grabbed a couple roots and pulled herself out of the finished hole.  There were now two holes.. perfect for hiding and grabbing the enemy.  Grabbing the broken limbs and leaves, she began to weave them into a hidden canopy for the hole.  Knelt down, there was a slight smile on her lips.  This was something a daughter of Ares was born for.  Preparing for prey...it was innate. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

"We ride tonight!  With the strength that Hera has given
us-- and the strength that we have _earned_ for ourselves!  Take
what you need, but be quick.  Stay only until the sound of horn.
The moment you hear it-- we ride away.  Now-- to your horses."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elektraamazon>Elektra Amazon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#993300>(2/27/03 10:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=72>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/ddelektradd/images/smelek.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The men.</span><hr size=1> Working on the other hole, Elektra slid some of her long spears inside.  Then began to weave a canopy for the second one.  As she did, she looked to Hippolyte.  &quot;May I have this one, Hippolyte?&quot;  She so loved being under the ground in these attacks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solariwolf@amazonsunite>solariwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Themiscryian War Queen</span><br>  Posts: 97<br> <font color=#993300>(2/27/03 10:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=73>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The men.</span><hr size=1> Solari was sitting at her table, reading over a scroll when her owl flew in and landed on the table. Solari knew something was up, as she had sent him after Hippolyte when she saw her. She stood up, grabbed her cloak and straped her broadsword onto her back. She walked outside and mounted up on her warhorse and whistled softly for her owl to join her. She quietly rode out of the villiage in the direction she sensed from her feathered friend. She rode in silence, hard and fast to where she was needed. She was barely tired when she entered the forest. Her owl was now flying from place to place, showing his master the way until he stopped. Solari quietly made her way towards the group digging the holes. <br>
 &quot;Hipployte.&quot; was all she said.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 798<br> <font color=#993300>(3/6/03 1:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=74>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The men.</span><hr size=1> Hipp looked up to see Solari and then smirked.  &quot;Well...yasoo Vasilissa Solari.  Did word get out to much of Themiscrya that you now seek to find out what we are up to far from home?&quot;<br>
She placed a dirty hand on her hip, a smile on her face. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

"We ride tonight!  With the strength that Hera has given
us-- and the strength that we have _earned_ for ourselves!  Take
what you need, but be quick.  Stay only until the sound of horn.
