 &quot;No, not at all. I just thought that perhaps you needed my help with the soldiers.&quot; She smiled softly, a hint of revenge glowing in her eyes. &quot;Besides, I have my own score to settle with the Romans.&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 800<br> <font color=#993300>(3/7/03 12:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=76>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Men</span><hr size=1> &quot;Then join us by all means, athelfi,&quot; Hipp smiled to Solari.  &quot;We are almost finished.  It seems those soldiers use this area as a pass.....&quot; <br>
